<h2>Engineering Rigor</h2>
<p>EDDI maintains <strong>exceptional code quality</strong> through comprehensive testing, static analysis, and CI/CD quality gates. Every pull request must pass the full test suite before merge.</p>

<h3>Quality Metrics</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>1,500+ Tests</strong> — Unit, integration, and end-to-end coverage</li>
<li><strong>Zero Failures</strong> — Clean CI on every build</li>
<li><strong>Checkstyle Enforcement</strong> — Reduced from 697 to 81 warnings</li>
<li><strong>MCP Tool Tests</strong> — Comprehensive coverage of all 39 MCP tools</li>
<li><strong>CI/CD Quality Gates</strong> — Automated checks prevent regressions</li>
</ul>

